(13, 16, 'admin', 'demo@demo.org', '', '192.168.9.78', '2015-05-25 11:52:47', '2015-05-25 11:52:47', 'Now I know what colors to choose for me office, thank you!', 0, '1', '', '', 11, 0),
(14, 17, 'admin', 'demo@demo.org', '', '192.168.9.78', '2015-05-25 11:51:14', '2015-05-25 11:51:14', 'Some of the basic ways by which we communicate with one another is through speech, sign language, body language, touch, and eye contact. So, waiting for the sequel of your post.', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
(15, 17, 'admin', 'demo@demo.org', '', '192.168.9.78', '2015-05-25 11:51:47', '2015-05-25 11:51:47', 'Indeed, it would be extremely hard to imagine a world without some form of interpersonal interaction.', 0, '1', '', '', 14, 0),
(16, 17, 'admin', 'demo@demo.org', '', '192.168.9.78', '2015-05-25 11:52:44', '2015-05-25 11:52:44', ' Communication is the process of exchanging information in the form of messages, symbols, thoughts, signs, and opinions. It’s utterly important for such social beings like people.', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
(17, 18, 'admin', 'demo@demo.org', '', '192.168.9.78', '2015-05-25 11:51:10', '2015-05-25 11:51:10', 'I thought I am just a dreamer, but now I know how to become a doer. That’s cool, appreciate it!.', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
(18, 18, 'admin', 'demo@demo.org', '', '192.168.9.78', '2015-05-25 11:51:42', '2015-05-25 11:51:42', 'Will try to repeat your mantras every day. Hopefully they will help in my current project.', 0, '1', '', '', 17, 0),
(19, 18, 'admin', 'demo@demo.org', '', '192.168.9.78', '2015-05-25 11:52:06', '2015-05-25 11:52:06', 'Follow your dream and it will turn to reality. A very inspiring article. Thanks for sharing!', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
(20, 19, 'admin', 'demo@demo.org', '', '192.168.9.78', '2015-05-25 11:32:06', '2015-05-25 11:32:06', 'Human life is the most precious thing in this world. It’s really time to stop committing lazy suicides.', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
(21, 19, 'admin', 'demo@demo.org', '', '192.168.9.78', '2015-05-25 11:52:30', '2015-05-25 11:52:30', 'Gosh! I have been slowly damaging my heart all these years! It’s time to stop ruining myself. ', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
(22, 19, 'admin', 'demo@demo.org', '', '192.168.9.78', '2015-05-25 11:53:10', '2015-05-25 11:53:10', 'Thanks for your pieces of advice. Will try to stick to them.', 0, '1', '', '', 20, 0),
(23, 20, 'admin', 'demo@demo.org', '', '192.168.9.78', '2015-05-25 11:32:02', '2015-05-25 11:32:02', 'He is phenomenal! Rumi is considered to be the most popular poet in America.', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
