(26, 21, 'admin', 'demo@demo.org', '', '192.168.9.78', '2015-05-25 11:31:59', '2015-05-25 11:31:59', 'Unbelievable… Three simple guidelines to follow that can change your life. Worth trying out, sure they will work as everything genius is simple.', 0, '1', '', '', 0, 0),
