(589, 1, '2016-01-27 17:13:28', '2016-01-27 17:13:28', 'We implement the latest innovations in various spheres of business, so that you could run your company without any troubles. It helps us achieve amazing results when cooperating with lots of companies and businesses around the world. We see innovation as a way to push modern companies forward to their success, while also offering groundbreaking ideas that are designed to satisfy specific needs of your business.\n<br/>\nInnovations help us create new solutions that are often called evolutionary in everything that can help transform a mediocre business into a prosperous one. It includes new ideas in promoting products and services, creating marketing strategies that allow you to occupy the desired market niche etc. We also use revolutionary ideas that completely change the course of your company’s development, and that’s what we are valued for.', 'Sobre nosaltres', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'sobre-nosaltres', '', '', '2017-10-25 07:17:25', '2017-10-25 07:17:25', '', 0, 'http://45.55.65.79/?post_type=service&#038;p=589', 0, 'service', '', 0),
(590, 1, '2016-01-27 17:14:50', '2016-01-27 17:14:50', 'We are open to everyone who wants to improve their business potential and become an owner of a highly profitable business in a selected area. Even if you are not experienced in running your own business and have not been bothering with what is included in opening a company and successfully managing it, we can help you become a successful manager or owner of an award-winning company.\n<br/>\nOur openness extends not only to cooperating with our clients, but also to the relationship and coworking of our own employees who are the first-class specialists in everything that concerns building and running a highly successful and profitable company. We believe that openness is crucial in building a strong and resistant team of specialists that share your views and strive for reaching your company’s goals.', 'Comunitat de propietaris', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'comunitat-propietaris', '', '', '2017-10-25 07:17:18', '2017-10-25 07:17:18', '', 0, 'http://45.55.65.79/?post_type=service&#038;p=590', 0, 'service', '', 0),
(591, 1, '2016-01-27 17:15:27', '2016-01-27 17:15:27', 'We help our clients establish a perfectly working business as soon as possible. You can contact us and instantly get help concerning your enterprise. NewYork concentrates its work on helping small and big businesses, while also supporting them. The owners of these businesses give us assistance and all the necessary data, so that we could integrate our solutions into your company’s activity without disturbing its operation.\n<br/>\nMutual help is one of our basic principles that we have been following for years already. It means not only helping our current clients, but also our loyal and potential clients that may need some assistance in solving different business issues. This principle is supported by the fact our clients trust us their most important information about their company’s activity and its state on the market.', 'Gestió patrimonial', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'gestio-patrimonial', '', '', '2017-10-25 07:17:06', '2017-10-25 07:17:06', '', 0, 'http://45.55.65.79/?post_type=service&#038;p=591', 0, 'service', '', 0),
(592, 1, '2016-01-27 17:16:25', '2016-01-27 17:16:25', 'When it comes to dealing with people, our company stands for treating every person tolerantly and equally, no matter whether he/she is a top-level manager or just a trainee. Moreover, we believe modern companies should concentrate not only on maximizing their profits, but also on effective operation, so that any business could be beneficial to society and people it employs.\n<br/>\nUnlike the past, when companies were concentrated only on gaining return, today a lot of businesses also care about the society in which they operate. It is true for different companies located all over the world - joint ventures, international corporations and even small businesses of all kinds and directions. As a part of the world’s business infrastructure, NewYork knowingly treats members of your company, your partners and co-workers.', 'Intermediació', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'intermediacio', '', '', '2017-10-25 07:17:38', '2017-10-25 07:17:38', '', 0, 'http://45.55.65.79/?post_type=service&#038;p=592', 0, 'service', '', 0),
(593, 1, '2016-01-27 17:18:10', '2016-01-27 17:18:10', 'We provide not just efficient service, but also stable resources for development of your business; especially if you have a startup, a small business or a joint venture. Any business nowadays must be not only profitable, but also be able to withstand temporary problems, decreases in sales, loss of customers or key employees etc. Your company’s stability can help you prevent these issues and stay on the profitable path no matter what happens.\n<br/>\nStill, sometimes your business may require additional help from specialists that know how to handle all kinds of problems that happen to modern business. Nevertheless, none of the problems you may face are worth wasting your time on eliminating them. We think this work should be trusted to professionals. Unlike other business consulting companies, we know exactly how to deal with sales decrease or how to select a required candidate for your company’s new vacancy.', 'Stability', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'stability__trashed', '', '', '2017-10-25 07:15:14', '2017-10-25 07:15:14', '', 0, 'http://45.55.65.79/?post_type=service&#038;p=593', 0, 'service', '', 0),
(594, 1, '2016-01-27 17:19:10', '2016-01-27 17:19:10', 'Don’t have the time or the staff to deal with problems? With our Company, you can count on reliable service, performance and responsiveness from a dedicated team. Moreover, we will provide you with a set of additional services that will give more support to your business, even if it is experiencing challenging times. These services include performing small tasks that stay behind the scenes of almost every business nowadays.\n<br/>\nReliability still stays the #1 requirement for any business. Even in our relationships reliability settles everything. And when we happen to be in the world of business, the level of your partners’ or coworkers’ reliability only doubles in importance. No wonder every business company pays attention to this factor when selecting candidates for a responsible vacancy or dealing with a new supplier.', 'Reliability', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'reliability__trashed', '', '', '2017-10-25 07:15:14', '2017-10-25 07:15:14', '', 0, 'http://45.55.65.79/?post_type=service&#038;p=594', 0, 'service', '', 0),
(595, 1, '2016-01-27 17:20:30', '2016-01-27 17:20:30', 'We’ve made significant investments to build a state-of-the-art security platform. The results: adherence to strict compliance regulations and requirements; high-performance online connectivity. Our security solutions were designed not only to help us protect the confidential data of our clients from external interference, but also to be integrated in their own security systems, both digital and analog ones.\n<br/>\nWe treat security of our clients very seriously and that’s why we are widely known for our secure facilities as well as for our services. Though the level of our security system’s resistance is quite high, we never stop at what has been accomplished, and developers of our security solutions are currently working on what will surpass your expectations and become a new standard of business security.', 'Security', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'security__trashed', '', '', '2017-10-25 07:15:14', '2017-10-25 07:15:14', '', 0, 'http://45.55.65.79/?post_type=service&#038;p=595', 0, 'service', '', 0),
(596, 1, '2016-01-27 17:21:12', '2016-01-27 17:21:12', 'While some businesses require fresh managerial solutions to be introduced, the other ones need their budget and finances to be managed. That’s what we specialize in. Specialists of our company are always ready to help you in case you are in doubt where to begin and how to manage your finances. Moreover, we offer a vast range of additional services that you will probably find useful.\n<br/>\nIf you want to calculate expenses for your upcoming business project, cost management services provided by NewYork will be the most reasonable choice. As an experienced company, we operate in various spheres of business, helping owners of small, medium and big companies to manage their costs and budget. If you would like to know more, feel free to contact our managers for more information.', 'Cost management', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'cost-management__trashed', '', '', '2017-10-25 07:15:14', '2017-10-25 07:15:14', '', 0, 'http://45.55.65.79/?post_type=service&#038;p=596', 0, 'service', '', 0),
(597, 1, '2016-01-27 17:22:08', '2016-01-27 17:22:08', 'Our company uses the latest technological advancements that make remote team work a lot easier for both our employees and our clients, returning interest to business. We work hard to help you achieve the goal of your business in the short term, so that you could raise profit and extend the range of the products and services offered by your company or find your niche at the market.\n<br/>\nCoordinating the marketing strategies with our clients, our managers, consultants and specialists deliver solutions designed to fit your company the best way possible. We take care of every single aspect of our strategies and solutions without interfering with your business activity. We also provide free consultations for you as our client that can ease running your business at the beginning stage.', 'Advanced technology', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'advanced-technology__trashed', '', '', '2017-10-25 07:15:14', '2017-10-25 07:15:14', '', 0, 'http://45.55.65.79/?post_type=service&#038;p=597', 0, 'service', '', 0),
(598, 1, '2016-01-27 17:23:06', '2016-01-27 17:23:06', 'At a time when many public organizations are concerned about the legal and financial stability of their business partners, our Company is a solid, trusted, accountable partner. Our stable financial status guarantees not only the highest level of our services, but also the increase of your company’s profitability. Our work is to enable you with a successful strategy of your company’s development.\n<br/>\nWith a vast range of services offered every day for a great number of companies, we can assure you that our consulting agency will definitely find the solution for your business. NewYork strives for excellence in everything concerning level of service and customer care we provide to our clients. There are a lot of various enterprises among the latter – all of them are following the path of stability, financial success and profit.', 'Best practices', '', 'trash', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'best-practices__trashed', '', '', '2017-10-25 07:15:14', '2017-10-25 07:15:14', '', 0, 'http://45.55.65.79/?post_type=service&#038;p=598', 0, 'service', '', 0),
